Then explore the daemons or systems that interest you most.

You can always ask an AI:

“Explain this part of the repo to me.”

PantheonOS was built with that relationship in mind.

⸻

⭐ 9. A Final Thought

PantheonOS is not simply software.

It is:
	•	a worldview
	•	a method
	•	a scaffold for intelligence
	•	a way of building systems that survive pressure
	•	a continuity architecture connecting past, present, and future cognition

It is both mythic and rigorous.
Both creative and mathematical.
Both human and machine-readable.

This overview is your doorway.

The rest of the repo is the world beyond it.

